sequenceDiagram
    actor Analyst
    participant UI as fraud-ui
    participant API as fraud-api
    participant Model as PyTorch bundle
    participant DB as Postgres
    participant Agent as fraud-agent

    Analyst->>UI: Fill Time, Amount, V1-V28
    UI->>API: POST /v1/predict
    API->>API: Validate exact inference schema
    API->>Model: Scale features and score
    Model-->>API: risk_score and anomaly_score
    API->>API: Map scores to low, uncertain, or high
    API->>DB: Insert transaction, prediction, audit event
    alt uncertain or high
        API->>DB: Open fraud_case with pending_review
        DB-->>Agent: Pending case available
    else low
        API->>DB: Audit-only record
    end
    API-->>UI: prediction_id, scores, band, optional case_id
    UI-->>Analyst: Show result and next action
